{"tid":2454140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果可以轉售年齡你賣唔賣？","createTime":"2021-03-20T04:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T08:35:15.000Z","uid":275238,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"99077aaa559081aacaa252626c81a6c6452b15e8","tid":2454140,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"有好多達官貴人想超過100歲嘅同時亦有好多窮撚想刷首抽<br />\n<br />\n講下規則先<br />\n1唔可以賣超過你自己年齡上限(本來有幾歲命)<br />\n2賣晒就會即時死亡<br />\n3唔可以互相買賣刷點數<br />\n4只可以買賣一次<br />\n5你唔會知自己年齡上限<br />\n譬如你依家係30歲本來有80歲命(但你唔會知)，可以賣50年，咁就會即時死亡，但如果只係賣40年，咁你就只能活到40歲，如此類推<br />\n<br />\n賣出嘅年齡將會影響你轉世刷首抽時能夠用嘅點數，點數轉換率係1：100，賣1年有100點<br />\n<br />\n選項需要點數<br />\n地區： 500-5000<br />\n人種： 100-10000<br />\n父母： 0-50000<br />\n運程： 0-100000<br />\n其他雜項： 0-500000<br />\n<br />\n冇點數就完全隨機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔賣"},{"pid":"047fbcda0472956a5819f253f32eae32255c0aeb","tid":2454140,"uid":140363,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"On撚9<br />\n<br />\n1年100點 你set到幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126d73a5efed124b38db0ff9f9db05d63a61433a","tid":2454140,"uid":275238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"047fbcda0472956a5819f253f32eae32255c0aeb","tid":2454140,"uid":140363,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"On撚9<br />\n<br />\n1年100點 你set到幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:43:02.000Z","msg":"幾十萬係做極級白人鬼佬，要修行或者刷幾十次支那或者非洲族先夠點數做㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8db1690224a95f581c31714e506c4dacc0af857","tid":2454140,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:46:05.000Z","msg":"不